{"title":"Zohar","link":"/en/wol/d/r1/lp-e/1200004759","html":"<span id=\"page1240\" class=\"pageNum\" data-no=\"1240\" data-before-text=\"1240\"></span><strong>ZOHAR</strong>(Zo&#x2B9;har).<strong>1. </strong>A Hittite whose son Ephron sold the cave of Machpelah to Abraham.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\">Ge 23:7-9;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/0/1\" data-bid=\"1-2\" class=\"b\"> 25:9</a>.<strong>2. </strong>Fifth-named son of Simeon and father of a tribal family; one of those numbered among the 70 of Jacob&#x2019;s household who &#x201C;came into Egypt.&#x201D; (<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Ge 46:8,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\"> 10,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/1/2\" data-bid=\"2-3\" class=\"b\"> 27;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/1/3\" data-bid=\"2-4\" class=\"b\"> Ex 6:15</a>) He is elsewhere called Zerah.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">Nu 26:13;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200004759/2/1\" data-bid=\"3-2\" class=\"b\"> 1Ch 4:24</a>."}